##### add a new animal
###
POST http://localhost:3000/add-animal?idir={{idir}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "animal_id": "test123",
  "animal_status": "Alive",
  "calf_at_heel": true,
  "species": "unicorn",
  "sex": "M",
  "wlh_id": "abc123",
  "nickname": "shimmer"
}

